title: Ashes archive: Labuschagne brings comedic relief with awful appeal
text:
Amid England's torrid previous Test tour of Australia, Marnus Labuschagne brings some much needed comedy relief to the fourth test with a hilarious appeal.

summary: Amid England's torrid previous tour of Australia, Marnus Labuschagne brought some much needed comedy relief to the fourth test with a hilarious appeal. Have you ever seen worse?
